&lt;color=#ebcaa2&gt;저, 그럼 보수는… 어떻게 드려야 할지… 저희가 돈이 없어서요…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ebcaa2&gt;But, um... how could we repay you...? We don't have much money...&lt;/color&gt;

