EN:
&lt;color=#ffef23&gt;Your running shoes look like they could fetch a nice price...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;무슨 소리. …는 돈을 받고 의를 행하지 않는다네!&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Fie on thee! A... ...doth not dole out justice based on promise of capital!&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;그래도 뭐, 정 도와주고 싶다면…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#cc2424&gt;Still, if thou truly wishest to help, then...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;이 기억은… 돈키호테… 인가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;This memory... Was that... Don Quixote...?&gt;
